		<td rowspan="2" class="Text_pane" style="height:100%;width:25%;background-color:#D7CB94;"><h2 style="font-size:145%;"><p>Solar Cookers World Network</p> </h2> <br /> <table> <tbody> <tr> <td valign="middle"><b>Formerly:&nbsp;&nbsp;</b> </td> <td valign="middle"><img alt="" style="width: 180px;" src="/images/scatitle_small.jpg" /></td> </tr> </tbody> </table> <br /> <p>SCI sponsors the <a href="http://solarcooking.wikia.com/wiki/Solar_Cookers_World_Network_(Home)" target="_blank">Solar Cookers World Network</a> (SCWNet), an alliance of more than 300 NGOs and individuals involved in promoting solar cooking. The SCWNet has created <a href="http://solarcooking.wikia.com/wiki/Solar_Cookers_World_Network_(Home)" target="_blank">a wiki-based site</a> that contains extensive information about all aspects of solar cooking.</p> <br /> <p><strong>See detailed solar cooking info by:</strong> </p> <br /> <ul style="padding-left: 20px;"> <li><a href="http://solarcooking.wikia.com/Countries" target="_blank">Country</a>  </li> <li><a href="http://solarcooking.wikia.com/NGOs" target="_blank">Non-governmental organization (NGO)</a>  </li> <li><a href="http://solarcooking.wikia.com/people" target="_blank">Individual</a>  </li> <li><a href="http://solarcooking.wikia.com/manu" target="_blank">Manufacturer or vendor</a>  </li> <li><a href="http://solarcooking.wikia.com/designs" target="_blank">Design</a> </li> <li><a href="http://solarcooking.wikia.com/Category:Browse" target="_blank">Category</a>  </li> </ul> <br /> <p><strong>Other topics:</strong> </p> <br /> <ul style="padding-left: 20px;"> <li><a href="http://solarcooking.wikia.com/wiki/Solar_Cookers_World_Network_(Home)" target="_blank">Latest solar cooking news</a> </li> <li><a href="http://solarcooking.org/Calendar_of_events" target="_blank">Calendar of Events</a> </li> <li><a href="http://solarcooking.wikia.com/Plans" target="_blank">Build a solar cooker </a></li> <li><a href="http://solarcooking.wikia.com/Buy" target="_blank"